msg.content:
As of my last data update in January 2023, here is a list of the judges serving on the US Supreme Court, along with their undergraduate degrees:

1. Sonia Sotomayor - Princeton University
2. Brett Kavanaugh - Yale University
3. Elena Kagan - Princeton University
4. Neil Gorsuch - Columbia University
5. Amy Coney Barrett - Rhodes College
6. Samuel Alito - Princeton University
7. Clarence Thomas - Holy Cross College
8. John Roberts - Harvard University
9. Ketanji Brown Jackson - Harvard University

Please note that undergraduate degrees are only one aspect of the educational background of these judges, and they have all completed further degrees and held various positions prior to joining the Supreme Court.
